    "name": "Policy API - Complete Workflow",
    "description": "Complete test suite for Policy Pillar\n\nBased on: specs/policy/policy.pillar.v2.yml (v2.3.0)\n\nv2.3.0 additions:\n- C7: Split Payment 50/50 — billing_type='split' creates 2 installments at 50% each\n- C7: billing_type='full' creates 1 upfront installment\n\nv2.2.0 additions:\n- M1: Deposit Capacity Formula — GET /deposit + POST /deposit/evaluate (re-derives from rate table)\n\nCovers:\n- M4: Package Auto-Selection (GET /package-lookup)\n- M1: Deposit Capacity Formula Enforcement\n- C7: Split Payment 50/50\n- Master data setup (packages, rates)\n- Policy creation and activation\n- Member management\n- Benefit usage (reserve → confirm → release)\n- Billing plan and installments\n- Deposit requirement evaluation\n- Remediation case management",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
